Void Func_Rcrsv()

{

Func_Rcrsv();

}

int main()

{

Func_Rcrsv (); return 0;

}

Response: The program will stop because of encountered overflow condition in stack. 

Correct : The program will stop because of encountered overflow condition in stack. 

